name: Frank NEWMAN et al. v. Patrick T. BOYLE et al.

parties: Frank NEWMAN et al. v. Patrick T. BOYLE et al.

opinions.text:
ORDER
The petitioners’ motion to quash the Superior Court injunction or in the alternative to stay the operation thereof as prayed is denied.
DORIS, J., did not participate.

attorneys: Letts, Quinn & Licht, Nicholas Trott Long, Daniel J. Murray, Joseph DeAngelis, Providence, for petitioners.
DeSimone & Del Sesto Law Corporation, Herbert F. DeSimone, Gerard McG. De-Celles, Providence, for respondents.
casebody.head_matter:
Frank NEWMAN et al. v. Patrick T. BOYLE et al.
No. 79-510-M.P.
Supreme Court of Rhode Island.
Dec. 28, 1979.
Letts, Quinn & Licht, Nicholas Trott Long, Daniel J. Murray, Joseph DeAngelis, Providence, for petitioners.
DeSimone & Del Sesto Law Corporation, Herbert F. DeSimone, Gerard McG. De-Celles, Providence, for respondents.
